Package: sir
Type: Package
Title: Social Influence Regression Models
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-08-11
Authors@R: c(
    person("Shahryar", "Minhas", email = "shahryar.minhas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Peter", "Hoff", email = "peter.hoff@duke.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements Social Influence Regression (SIR) models for analyzing 
    network data with social influence effects. The package provides efficient 
    methods for fitting models with bilinear effects using either Alternating 
    Least Squares (ALS) or direct optimization approaches. Supports Poisson, 
    Normal, and Binomial outcome distributions.
